I would ask for the mechanical one because of the pressure issues .
Then, if yoy decide down the road to go to fuel injection you can buy the FI
pump.
If you dont ask for the mechanical one they may send you a case that doen't
have the hole milled for it, then you only have one choice.
Also if you do end up running a low pressure electric one for any reason,
get one with adjustable pressure.
I believe Bugpack makes em.
Good luck
Beian
